{"tid":820040,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［勸世］佛系情侶同我入一入黎","createTime":"2018-09-15T08:04:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T06:53:05.000Z","uid":186163,"like":5,"dislike":52,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"29f0e13bd2d42bc27c7640b5082ce44a426f38b5","tid":820040,"uid":186163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:04:12.000Z","msg":"現任係我初戀<br />\n最初識既時候<br />\n大家既相處好正常<br />\n亦都係有機會發展既另一半<br />\nWhatsapp會曖味<br />\n一星期都會見一次<br />\n不過果陣都有d佛系<br />\n對方表白後<br />\n最初<br />\n大家既相處方式都一樣（有d佛系）<br />\n<br />\n慢慢地<br />\n基於種種原因<br />\n可能係因為我太負能量<br />\n但我一直都係心平氣和咁講<br />\n亦都可能因為佢工作忙碌<br />\n亦都可能因為大家唔夠愛大家<br />\n<br />\nWhatsapp愈傾愈少<br />\n最後變成n日無搵過對方...<br />\n<br />\n同對方討論過佛系既問題<br />\n但佢俾d佛系答案我<br />\n我真係唔知可以俾咩反應佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n呢段關係<br />\n我承認我都有錯<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">但我依加又可以點？</span><br />\n<br />\n真心勸大家唔好佛系拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我知你會上連登，你都知我ac..."},{"pid":"89ba824908b40cfa32d652724aaefd0aaca78bdd","tid":820040,"uid":62471,"like":76,"dislike":0,"score":76,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:05:01.000Z","msg":"佛乜撚野系<br />\n出家做和尚啦佛系"},{"pid":"c8fea01fd87c5667f3fe7ab55fa497a2ad218006","tid":820040,"uid":100988,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:05:13.000Z","msg":"You up mid chun"},{"pid":"103467e1c08b00e938aaab5a01d119dead306540","tid":820040,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:06:00.000Z","msg":"佛系<br />\n簡單d講姐係冇性生活？"},{"pid":"6f2292c8ff55c4efcbb928e9643cf9e52d6bf3cd","tid":820040,"uid":129739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-15T08:06:08.000Z","msg":"你唔想做佛系，咪做食肉系。飛起佢，做肉食女吧。"},{"pid":"1b16a718d29b297367b2b63f820e0a01074e253c","tid":820040,"uid":31374,"like":3,"dis